 projects for clients during a gap between contracts in  the two began work on a microblogging website which was launched as tumblr in february  as of june   tumblr hosts over  million blogs in august  karp was named best young tech entrepreneur  by businessweek and in  he was named to the mit technology review tr as one of the top  innovators in the world under the age of  on may   it was announced that yahoo and tumblr had reached an agreement for yahoo to acquire tumblr for  billion karp remained ceo of the company contents  early life  career  advocacy  personal life  references  external links early lifeedit born in new york city karp grew up on the upper west side of manhattan his parents are barbara ackerman a science teacher from san anselmo california and michael d karp a film and television composer he has a younger brother named kevin his parents separated when he was  karp attended the calhoun school from aged three through th grade where his mother teaches science at  he began learning html and was soon designing websites for businesses karp went on to attend bronx science for one year before dropping out at the age of  and started homeschooling at the time karp had aspirations of getting into a college in new york or mit and saw homeschooling and doing other projects on the side as a way to impress the colleges karp never returned to high school or earned his high school diploma marco arment the first employee of tumblr would later recall that karp was keen to avoid letting his age shape peoples assumptions about him he wanted to keep it quiet for as long as he could because he knew that as soon as it got out every story about tumblr would just be about davids youth careeredit karp in  karp began interning at age  for animation producer fred seibert founder of frederator studios karps mother had taught seiberts children at the calhoun school and was friends with his wife karp was fascinated with the work of frederators computer engineers and his visits became regular after he started homeschooling karp also began taking japanese classes at the japan society and saw a math tutor with whom he worked on writing software for winning at blackjack and poker when entrepreneur john maloney sought technical help with urbanbaby an online parenting forum a frederator employee recommended karp for the job karp completed the project which had to be done in a couple of days within four hours maloney made him urbanbabys head of product and gave him a small amount of equity at age  while still working for urbanbaby karp moved alone to tokyo for five months it was a full three months after karp had moved to tokyo that urbanbaby found out he wasnt in new york i realized that i got to spend that entire day working on this product that i absolutely loved  and it was this incredible liberating unbelievably inspiring feeling “ ” —karp in an interview with fast company about his first day of work dedicated solely to tumblr karp left urbanbaby after it was sold to cnet in  using money from the sale of his shares karp started his own software consultancy company davidville envisioning a mix of client work and his own products marco arment joined the company as an engineer after replying to karps craigslist ad karp had been interested in tumblelogs shortform blogs for some time and was waiting for one of the established blogging platforms to introduce their own tumblelogging platform as no one had done so after a year of waiting karp and arment began working on their own tumblelogging platform during a twoweek gap between contracts in  tumblr was launched in february  and within two weeks the service had gained  users in october  karp shut down his consultancy business as his work with tumblr was interfering with his client work davidville was renamed tumblr inc and  percent of the company was sold to a small group of investors on may   it was announced that yahoo and tumblr had reached an agreement for yahoo to acquire tumblr for  billion karp remained as ceo as of june   tumblr hosts over  million blogs advocacyedit karp joined the planned parenthood board of directors in  in march  tumblr and planned parenthood launched an initiative calling on the tech industry to support planned parenthood karp endorsed hillary clinton for president in the leadup to the  united states election personal lifeedit beginning in  karps girlfriend was rachel eakley a psychology graduate and nursing student they lived together in williamsburg with their pet dog clark the pair split in  karp has made personal investments into several companies including superpedestrian inc the company behind the copenhagen wheel sherpaa inc a healthcare app startup and splash an event marketing platform referencesedit  a b c bercovici jeff january   tumblr david karps  million art project forbes retrieved january     a b davis sammy august   so what do you do david karp founder of tumblr mediabistrocom archived from the original on january   retrieved january     a b kushner david november   david karp is the barely legal blogfather maxim archived from the original on january   retrieved january     a b c d e f g shafrir doree january   would you take a tumblr with this man the new york observer archived from the original on january   retrieved january     david karp reminds me of ted turner may   fredseibertfrederatorcom  retrieved    a b about us tumblr retrieved june     best young tech entrepreneurs  tumblr bloomberg businessweek retrieved december     a b ingram matthew august   google vc tumblr ceo among the top innovators under  gigaom giga omni media archived from the original on january   retrieved january     new computer mogul tumblr founder karp has family roots in marin  san jose mercury news mercurynewscom retrieved on   a b c d e f g walker rob july   can tumblrs david karp embrace ads without selling out the new york times magazine archived from the original on january   retrieved january     bercovici jeff interviewer 