trieved february     eakley rachel february   i get the feeling library sciences archived from the original on march   retrieved march     parker ashley september   kill the alarm and rev up the vespa the new york times archived from the original on june   retrieved january     eakley rachel november   this stuff is so strange and sweet and strange library sciences retrieved december     chernova yuliya march   tumblrs david karp giving back to ny startups but dont call him a vc the wall street journal archived from the original on march   retrieved march     chernova yuliya march   tumblr founder david karp invests in medicaltreatment startup sherpaa venture capital dispatch the wall street journal archived from the original on march   retrieved january     crook jordan december   splash transitions to bb event marketing with m in new funding techcrunch archived from the original on january   retrieved january    external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to david karp david karps tumblr david karp on internet movie database the way i work david karp of tumblr article by liz welch inc magazine david karp is tumblrs reluctant technologist article by tim wu t the new york times style magazine authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitledavidkarpoldid categories  birthsstcentury american businesspeopleamerican technology chief executivesamerican technology company foundersbusinesspeople from new york cityliving peoplepeople from manhattanpeople from williamsburg brooklynthe bronx high school of science alumniyahoo peopleplanned parenthoodhidden categories articles with hcardswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikip